  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 9th level, you can touch a metal or stone weapon (or up to 50 pieces of ammunition) as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Standard-Actions\">standard action</a>, giving it the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic-items/magic-weapons#TOC-Bane\">bane</a>&nbsp;property against any creature with the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Earth\">earth</a>&nbsp;subtype,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Ooze\">oozes</a>, or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Construct\">constructs</a>&nbsp;made of stone or metal, for 1 minute. You can use this ability once per day at 9th level, twice per day at 17th, and three times per day at 20th.</p>"
